{"tid":2285894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【聽證會】滑鼠娘娘：德國聯署update","createTime":"2020-11-14T13:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T16:22:31.000Z","uid":138409,"like":99,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b6281baf07f89daccd2442fe6a30e1934b3a0f19","tid":2285894,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=10158630684532777&amp;set=a.70893087776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D10158630684532777%26set%3Da.70893087776&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=f3b58787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=10158630684532777&amp;set=a.70893087776</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/125411182_10158630684537777_4373712122480617512_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=8n1chOYTzuoAX_JahYm&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=2ecb9d12854d575cca51138cefb0eddb&amp;oe=5FD3EF30\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F125411182_10158630684537777_4373712122480617512_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D8n1chOYTzuoAX_JahYm%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D2ecb9d12854d575cca51138cefb0eddb%26oe%3D5FD3EF30&h=448d7c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n响10月嘅時候，我哋已經成功收集到過50K簽名，達到舉辦聽證會嘅門欖。 而响尋日，我哋終於收到德國國會嘅正式文件，<span class=\"gold\">確認我哋獲得聽證會嘅資格。不過聽證會日子仍然有待通知。</span><br />\n<br />\n响收到封信之前我都淆淆地，因為個網頁一直都冇出到meet quorum嘅字眼，加上呢個聯署出街都已經困難重重，都有少少擔心會出啲岔子。不過，而家收到信就無事了。 <br />\n<br />\n至於聽證會嘅日子會係幾時，我哋都未知道。因為武漢肺炎爆發第二波嘅關係，德國兩星期前已經進入咗lockdown狀態，雖然政府部門仲運作緊，但應該都唔會响lockdown期間舉辦聽證會。<span class=\"gold\">所以自己估計可能都要下年年頭先會有聽證會了。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然比預期中時間遲咗，但只要係德國下年大選之前可以舉行到，其實效果唔會差好遠。响聽證會上面，我希望可以反映到 #save12hkyouths 嘅重要性、香港已經所剩無幾嘅自由、政制崩壞等等嘅問題，亦都希望委員會嘅議員可以响中國議題上表態；聽證會亦都係德國選舉前，其中一個正式討論中國問題嘅場合，希望可以令到更加多人關注中國議題，同關心台灣新疆等地嘅問題。 <br />\n<br />\n聽證會未必可以好似神燈咁實現香港人嘅願望，但會係光復呢個過程嘅其中一小步。聽證會之後我哋會盡力促成更多嘅follow up，希望德國會更加強硬對中國。 <br />\n<br />\n要光復香港，唔係可以靠其他人，唔駛付出就可以完成。能夠連結到國際社會係好事，但我哋自己都要知道自己屋企一定要自己救。依賴其他地方，只會令香港跌落不停被其他國家影響、操控嘅循環入面。而光復香港之前，都請各位光復自己，照顧好自己。"},{"pid":"1a3058619e062c376cb97b6e75ba43e632f67c48","tid":2285894,"uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">確認我哋獲得聽證會嘅資格</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e581a8733435e1a17986aa66862bd6123b975a85","tid":2285894,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06d4637a70793d7df3ecca6a490687985dcf0805","tid":2285894,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":45,"score":-44,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a31f57fde351ffe4ddd3702528d4ef810b08738","tid":2285894,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21fe5872af868fa27e2180d3271ab0a3e260e04b","tid":2285894,"uid":138409,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"06d4637a70793d7df3ecca6a490687985dcf0805","tid":2285894,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":45,"score":-44,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"無衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaed4da7cf1b46dfa3b0cde81e08e6e631c36b7f","tid":2285894,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5d30fd862df736e2c12a9ea2432d059547953a7","tid":22858